OL,5, The state pension is rising by 8.5% on 
OL,6, Monday, because of a measure known as  
OL,7, the triple lock.                       
OL,9,FIt means that pensioners receive an    
OL,10,Famount designed to keep up with rising 
OL,11,Fprices or wage increases.              
OL,13,FThe state pension is a payment made    
OL,14,Fevery four weeks by the government, to 
OL,15,Fpeople who have reached the qualifying 
OL,16,Fage and have paid enough National      
OL,17,FInsurance contributions.               
